---
import MenuEN from '../../../components/MenuEN.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import Analytics from '../../../components/Analytics.astro';
import '../../../sass/general.scss';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>By plane, over Bilene</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Bilene Kite Center blog: our instructor flies from Maputo to Bilene in a Cessna">
    <Analytics />
</head>
<body>
    <MenuEN />

    <main>
        <div class="blog-hero">
            <img src="/images/blog/blog.webp" alt="blog Bilene Kite Center">
            <div class="blog-hero-overlay">
                <span class="blog-date">February 2026</span>
                <h1>Flooding? No problem!</h1>
            </div>
        </div>

        <article class="blog-article">
            <h2>Our Instructor Arrives in Style: Maputo to Bilene by Cessna!</h2>
            <p>
                This season, our instructor made his way to Bilene from Maputoâ€¦ <strong>aboard a small Cessna</strong>! An arrival that perfectly reflects the spirit of adventure and passion that drives the entire Bilenekite team.
            </p>
            <p>
                A flight over Mozambique's breathtaking landscapes, between turquoise lagoons and wild lands, to land right on our kite spot. <em>Because here, even the journey is part of the experience!</em>
            </p>
            <p>
                Ready to experience thrills (and chill) yourself? Join us for unforgettable sessions, on land and in the air!
            </p>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/pierro_73/reel/DTySK87DkTV/">Pierrot's video</a>
            <p>See you on the water!</p>
            <img src="/images/blog/avion.webp" alt="blog Bilene Kite Center" class="blog-img">
            <a href="/en/blog" class="blog-back">&larr; Back to blog</a>
        </article>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
    .blog-hero {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: 560px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    .blog-hero img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }
    .blog-hero-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.7));
        color: white;
    }
    .blog-hero-overlay h1 {
        font-size: 2.4em;
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }
    .blog-hero-overlay .blog-date {
        font-size: 0.9em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .blog-article {
        max-width: 750px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .blog-article p {
        font-size: 1.05em;
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: left;
        color: #444;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .blog-img {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .blog-back {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background: #4695fc;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .blog-back:hover {
        background: #3578d8;
    }
    .blog-back:visited {
        color: white;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .blog-hero {
            height: 350px;
        }
        .blog-hero-overlay h1 {
            font-size: 1.6em;
        }
    }
</style>
